Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(360.238,35,360.238,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23v\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:10.65,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(539.237,126)}CHARGE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.32,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}CRO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:11.99,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}MAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.28,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}TIE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:18.83,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs52\c&H111111&\3c&H111111&\pos(354,380)}Charge!! Cromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:30.02,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord1\blur1\c&H4040E7&v\pos(106,400)}First
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:35.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(500,0)}Cromartie Municipal High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:36.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}"Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"\Nhas finally been adapted as anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:46.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord1.7\pos(449.766,385)\shad0}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:54.34,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord1.7\pos(449.766,385)\shad0\c&HFDE2FC&\3c&HB450B1&}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fscx124.62\fnGilles' Comic Font\be1\bord4\pos(449.766,385)\fs32\shad0\c&HC9F0B1&\3c&H519302&}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.68,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,320)\be1\bord1.7\pos(449.766,385)\shad0}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}However, when the original work is a manga\Nand is adapted as anime afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I hear that there are people\Nwho complain about things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:46.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}such as character design and voice\Nactor casting. So I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:49.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}that I might as well play my role\Nwith this kind of face and voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:54.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}It may surprisingly be accepted\Nwithout any problems, pyo. Or,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it may be fine just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.42,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnNeon\fs32\b0\c&H1B1514&\bord0\blur0.5\frz-2\pos(242.443,128)}Tabata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I think I'll settle with this way after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is getting tiresome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Those who grumble should watch\Nthis anime 1000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I said anime, but there's hardly\Nbeen any movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:09.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs85\fnEdo SZ\c&HF0F0F0&\pos(207.323,441)}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(500,0)\fs50\fnNobody's Perfect\c&HF0F0F0&\pos(471.291,481)}of the introduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:18.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\shad0\c&H233555&\3c&H5A798E&\be4\frz7.845\t(\fs25)\frx13\fry345\move(617.437,232,594.778,233,24,5946)}Cromartie\N High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,One day, after being talked into it\Nby my classmate, Hayashida,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I came to Year 1 Class 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's trouble, Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a sober voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that Sugawara from our school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,got into a fight with guys\Nfrom Destrade High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:37.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. We just gotta round up\Nsome guys and fight 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He made a "ka-chink" noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, Sugawara was the one\Nwho started it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have a friend in Des-High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This'll be resolved if an apology\Nis made through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you suggesting we punk out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}Don't worry. I won't disgrace\NCromartie High school's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:57.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\move(1042.278,395,-271.899,395,0,7050)\c&HD9D9D9&\be2\q2}"Punk Out" One of the terms used by delinquents... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll make it so that I punked out all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:02.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why do you always take the role of the fall guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're actually pretty tough, Mechazawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but if you act like that, everyone\Nwill think you're a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're such a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They depend on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you not to\Ndo things that are bad for your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mechazawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I couldn't control myself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even then, you must control yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:34.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but who'll take care of your mother\Nif you're not around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa is more worried\Nabout you than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're being so dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No doubts about it, Mechazawa's\Nthe head of our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:44.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're no match for Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's oiling himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mechazawa. There's a little\Nsomething I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's something that's been bugging me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,since I saw you for the first time\Nafter entering this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is he finally gonna say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone in this class is probably\Nthinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I think everyone in the society\Nnotices it when they see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I even think that you possibly know about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or, I mean to say, don't you realize it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just be frank. What do you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No... Well... It's kinda hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:27.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think of you as my own family.\NI won't mind, no matter what you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:28.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then we'll tell it to you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Just go ahead and say it. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then I'll tell you, Mechazawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The second button on your\Nschool uniform is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No kidding. I hadn't noticed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's been bugging me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.47,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord0\frz10\fs50\c&H3C41D5&\blur0.4\shad3\an3\pos(475.823,307)\frx8\fry348}Blade Runner's\N High
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:56.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This CD player broke again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you take it to a repair shop,\Nit'll cost you big bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's someone who can fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course not, you idiot!\NOur school is full of dumb-asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:09.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's usually someone in a class\Nwho's good with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Someone who's good with machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.66,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an1\be2\pos(115.557,388)}Year 1\NClass 5            Shinichi Mechazawa (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can you fix this CD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm no good with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No good with machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa, can I talk to you a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've never been any good with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't do this video setting,\Nno matter how much I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, can you just set up\Nthe timer for the recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:40.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I said that's impossible!\NI'm poor with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:47.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But why do you all ask me about\N fixing machines or how to operate machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You asking why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, you take good care of your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:55.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'd like to do\Nwhatever you ask me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm even ready to risk my life for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I can't do machines, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow we felt that you\Nwere good with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's simply prejudice, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For example, people said stuff like\N "women are not good at machines" a while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but that's nothing but simple prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now cell phones and e-mails are trendy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and women handle them more\Nbeautifully than men, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At least they're a few dozen\Ntimes smarter than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:30.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, it wouldn't be good to decide\Non things according only to such prejudices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's oiling himself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:39.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I don't like a digitized world that's a result\Nof people depending too much on machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If there is no heart to heart communication\Namong people, in the end, I think it feels empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:46.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The way things are going,\N we'll all be controlled by machines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that he's joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:58.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's one thing that's been bugging me\Nsince I saw you for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:05.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Every time I see you, it bugs me so much lately\Nthat I can't even sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,ls he finally going to say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure everyone else\Nis bothered by it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't easy to tell you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:16.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Telling you this could possibly hurt your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Say it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! Say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay. Listen carefully,\N since I'll say it only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've got a big face, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Very close, but that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.64,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(20,0)\fnNeon\bord0.5\be1\b0\pos(358,65)\fs48\c&H1EC9CE&}Lost in Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(348.937,390)}Shinichi Mechazawa (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You've been doin'\Nwhatever the hell you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't make light of Bass High!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, Kamiyama!\NMechazawa's been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll go save him right away, Kamiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, hold on, Hayashida.\NWe shouldn't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:56.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that they'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:08:00.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! Then it'd be better\Nto watch from here as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He can take quite a beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're going to apologize, now is the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can't take me out with those little attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What was that, jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kamiyama, I just had a very scary thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could it be that we're the only ones\Nwho wonder about Mechazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:25.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everyone, except us, think Mechazawa\Nis an ordinary delinquent high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:30.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But no matter how you see him, he doesn't look\Nlike an ordinary delinquent high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or rather, he doesn't even\N look like a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll fudgin' kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're gonna pay you back for\Nwhat you've done to us, Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Does that possibly mean that there is\Nsomething wrong with our senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Mechazawa is just an ordinary\N16 year old high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This dumb-ass has got\N himself a pretty big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I now feel\Nthat there are people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You see? There should be guys like him if we\Nhang around the Shibuya Center Shopping Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not good. Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I've snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\c&&HE3E4DE&\fs42\bord0.2\be4\frz350\pos(94.032,455)}Drum Can
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, he really isn't a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NMy Strawberry Short blade got broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! You said your\NStrawberry Short blade got broken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:26.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All this time, we all thought that Mechazawa\Nwas an ordinary high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it could be that he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good, there's a normal guy here! Say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A high school student whose body\Nis abnormally hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! His body is unreasonably hard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:47.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are there none among you\N brave enough to fight me one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:53.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So in the end, you punks\N can't even fight without your buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's too much to ask\Nfrom you petty gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he's talking cool as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yokoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It may be true that there aren't\Nany sort of rules for fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but why don't you at least follow\Nthe basic principles of fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's that? Don't you think it's disgraceful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:18.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Five or six people ganging up on one guy,\Ntying him up, and beating him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, it's just us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What about your pride as students of Bass High?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look at this guy! You did too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! This man will say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... he's... ro... ro... ro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Almost there! Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Roly-poly" Mechazawa,\Nmy classmate from sixth grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Are you Yocchan, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:44.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(577.785,467)}To be\N\N\N continued
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel like the "Sakigake!! Cromartie High\NSchool" anime has been airing for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? This was only the second episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The next one is the third episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'll be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:48.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To be continued.
